reviewText: This was a gift. We love it!!

I really do enjoy these DVD's and they are very informative and very easy to understand and comprehend. He backs up what he says with bible verses and evidence from a scientific perspective. This should be on a " I have to watch this" list. Now, he is very sassy, but I just look past that and look at the truths he is teaching. He may not have a PHD or is a scientist but he is using God's word which, God is the ultimate scientist. Love these DVD's and I look forward to giving them to others to spread truth.
